{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM07_130.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hey, you're late."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Really late. We were waiting for so long."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Meklet! Atomina!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "...Damn it. We didn't make it in time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "From that tone, it sounds like you finally remembered who we are."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "And you had completely forgotten about us until now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You expected this, so you put your soul in that book, but you forgot all the important details. How laughable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Although it was a little beyond our predictions that you would forget about the Key of Truth too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I guess that's another thing to add to the list that we need to thank Sophie for."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Not only did you bring back Plachta's memories, but you made the Key for us too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. It's all thanks to you, Sophie, that we were able to reach the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, you're a really nice person. Unlike a certain someone there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, seriously. She went so far as to turn us into these things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "We couldn't use alchemy, and we couldn't go back to normal. We couldn't even age and die."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Living in these bodies for the last 500 years was torture."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "But our pain finally ends today. That's because..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x29,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Our wish will finally be fulfilled."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Our wish will finally be fulfilled."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It has been quite some time since I met you in this form, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Luard...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Your form has changed quite a bit since then. Now that I am my former self, it seems our positions have been reversed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1d,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "That doesn't matter. If it's been reversed, I just have to turn you back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Your demeanor certainly hasn't changed. However, I could care less. I simply wish to pursue alchemy, as I see fit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I know our reunion was short... But farewell."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Stop, Luard!!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Plachta..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "...Let's return to the atelier, Sophie. I'll tell you everything there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Okay..."
        }
    ]
}